Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we don't want to waste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to use it to the best advantage for oneself and for all of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
