Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in psychoanalysis, I can tell you the value of dreams from various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, in psychoanalysis, it was a critical part.
