Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The purpose of that was to increase one's understanding of the unconscious ego, which was a rare opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, he never wrote any.
