Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a knowingness that arises out of the frequency of the vibration
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of what you've picked up over some lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be 20 lifetimes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But somewhere you picked up the frequency and the vibration of that in your aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it's needed, it comes forth with a knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, that knowingness has to come from absolute conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The conviction has to be absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Absoluteness can only be conveyed by that which has walked through it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,walked through the hail and walked out the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So it can't be gotten out of oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it can only be gotten by that which has survived it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The value of 12-step groups is the sponsor is one who's walked through it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and come out the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest you can read out of a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people who go to those meetings have already read the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The book didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But when somebody stands there who's lived through it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,then they have the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And from them you get the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, you give it to the same power to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the value of the sponsor, the mentor, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,one who's lived it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll take my shoes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious, when you bless food or people or anything for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You said something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I'm curious, when you bless food or people or anything for that matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what technique do you use and how do you suggest that we would bless things and people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I look at it with love and gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Gratitude and consciously thank God for the gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you bless it in the name of,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you bless the food in the name of God for gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, you know, blessed food,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness calibration of the food itself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,jumps 15, 20 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So before you feed your kitty,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you're supposed to bless the kitty's food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless this kitty's food, oh Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:18:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Our cat's clairvoyant already, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep blessing her food every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,365 days a year, you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,she's starting to walk on water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And gratitude, you know, itself, bless this, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to be grateful for one's life, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the steward of your own life and its assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's nothing wrong with being rich and powerful at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, as long as you accept it with the humility
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that now this is your responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to be the rich king, to be whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, one of the most famous successful men
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in our society,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole society, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,gave $26 billion to charity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,$26 billion to charity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's more than the whole output
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of some whole country's $26 billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So out of gratitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,he tries to pay back to society
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in some way, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,College dropout at that, $26 billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, he dropped out of Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of names right now, you know, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Scottish guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Scottish guy or Microsoft?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Microsoft guy, Bill Gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Gates?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gates, yeah, yeah, Bill Gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I hold this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:19:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You may, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When, at the beginning, when you came down
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and you were shaking people's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you came near me, I just started to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering, why was I,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you were talking the rest of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even hardly listen, all I could do was cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering what that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what was going on for me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,or what was going on for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's common, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a certain level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,where you cry all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Monasteries are used to that, convents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You reach a certain level of lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and you cry all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remember going through that stage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would see a couple in the airport look at each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,just a loving glance, and it would just break me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The tears would come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of some kind of joy, you know, it's like joy, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:21:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of love makes you weep, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember in Scotland at the Tattoo, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,when they played a certain song, it was incredibly beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,a hundred bagpipes playing at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody in the audience crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole audience crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,18,000 people all crying at once, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you hit the heart of humanity, the heart of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You access the heart of man, you know, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and everybody weeps, you know, mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your books are getting heavier, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She says we should make smaller books so they don't weigh so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And talking about respect for all creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I find myself, you know, thinking about, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,myself, I'll find an ant or a spider in the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and I walk the little guys outside so they'll be happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day I saw a carpenter ant come across my wooden house floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Carpenter ant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.46,0:22:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Carpenter ant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is not an extermination question,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but it does seem that when you're talking about respect for creation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.46,0:22:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,calling in an exterminator to kill the guys does seem a little unkind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's his karma, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.46,0:22:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess the question would be what does that mean to my karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Death is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Death is not a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Life can only change form.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you change it out of this form here and it'll instantly emerge elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field, the energy of life cannot be extinguished through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.46,0:22:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot extinguish life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.46,0:22:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you didn't kill anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.46,0:22:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't kill anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:22:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:22:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.46,0:22:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think of all the excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.46,0:23:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets reborn in a better house with more crumbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.46,0:23:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Crumbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ants love crumbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is enlightenment a possibility from the inner planes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.46,0:23:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is enlightenment a possibility from the inner planes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.46,0:23:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
