Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.74,0:36:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,please speak why are you crying because I'm worried that I'm not crying I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.22,0:36:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,recreating stop crying so we can please tell me what it is you want to know stop
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.98,0:36:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the crying okay got no time right now for crying tell me what it is you want
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.63,0:37:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to know I can't no it wasn't it wasn't it was I wasn't asleep it was just sort
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.59,0:37:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of contemplating it the next day there's this focus and then it seems like the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.71,0:37:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,focus and this just massive energy just like merged yeah and then there's just
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.44,0:37:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,um
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.53,0:37:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,um
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.55,0:37:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,um
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.57,0:37:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,um
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.59,0:37:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,um
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.61,0:37:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,uninform you go from forum to nonform
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.59,0:37:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you got to stop crying now if you want to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.11,0:37:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,talk otherwise you can have to move on
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.40,0:37:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,okay stop the crying the power exercise
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.92,0:37:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the power control it's no time for the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.05,0:37:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,child to be coming up as the adult what
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.09,0:37:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,are you asking me is there is there a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.94,0:37:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,reality basis for that phenomena my
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.51,0:37:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding of the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.59,0:37:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is that your conception, definition of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.51,0:37:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,experience of yourself is linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.94,0:38:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It now comes up the alternate of the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.44,0:38:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not circumscribed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.86,0:38:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea of that which you are becomes obliterated
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.90,0:38:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,by a non-linear. Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.96,0:38:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.36,0:38:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why worry about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.90,0:38:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the lectures are all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.01,0:38:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dismissed. Case dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.59,0:38:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a premonition, yeah, a premonition
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.01,0:38:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that the eclipse of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.98,0:38:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.81,0:38:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.03,0:38:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing that thing where you feel pain
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.90,0:38:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and you increase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.15,0:38:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You try to get it to come out more or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.03,0:38:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Which gets pretty painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.88,0:38:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.59,0:38:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,lately I've been getting sensations
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.77,0:39:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,like tightness in the chest or something
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.48,0:39:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll go into that while I'm meditating
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.03,0:39:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll increase that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.67,0:39:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and it seems to come up into the throat
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.50,0:39:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and kind of get lodged in the throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.25,0:39:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't necessary to increase it, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.71,0:39:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only necessary to not resist it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.01,0:39:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And not say anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.44,0:39:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not define it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.13,0:39:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.59,0:39:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just a sensual sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.92,0:39:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stop resisting it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.29,0:39:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it will leave a specific area.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.05,0:39:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll know that you've stopped resisting it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.00,0:39:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because it becomes generalized in your whole aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.50,0:39:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You trip and you feel like you've sprained your ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.71,0:39:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in your ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.90,0:39:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As you let go of resisting it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.31,0:39:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the pain becomes diffuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.88,0:39:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like your whole aura experiences it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.03,0:39:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore you surrender to whatever that is
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.57,0:39:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,without calling it pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.59,0:39:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Or any other label.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.42,0:39:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you do, you finally disappear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.17,0:40:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you walk up and stand up and walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.29,0:40:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.65,0:40:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems like when I'm doing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.46,0:40:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be doing it wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.48,0:40:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but it comes up and it comes up into the throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.36,0:40:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.13,0:40:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And it'll stay there for a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.65,0:40:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I will cough pretty violently.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.09,0:40:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I get a sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.86,0:40:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of like I'm getting knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.55,0:40:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, like I don't feel the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.65,0:40:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I think sometimes the body twitches and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.50,0:40:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just get really real...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.15,0:40:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know if it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.67,0:40:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not numb, but it's more like tingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.73,0:40:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't know if I'm really healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.11,0:40:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.44,0:40:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So is this some energy you're resisting,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.65,0:40:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words, what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.88,0:40:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, like something...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.69,0:40:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting it caught in your throat?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.81,0:40:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.13,0:40:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, like something will come up,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.36,0:40:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,like a tightness in my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.19,0:40:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can try breathing the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.92,0:40:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,up to the crown chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.31,0:40:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Try that next.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.94,0:40:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.79,0:40:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And it kind of gets stuck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.05,0:40:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll cough.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.44,0:40:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it in the throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.53,0:40:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I said the crown chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.05,0:40:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but when it kind of gets stuck in here
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.96,0:41:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's not going to the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.00,0:41:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You breathe it up to the crown chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.86,0:41:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, instead of coughing it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.22,0:41:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.88,0:41:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.01,0:41:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you calibrate me
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.59,0:41:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and contextualize myself as being enlightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.92,0:41:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.44,0:41:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worth a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.11,0:41:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.51,0:41:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, when you're complete and total,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.38,0:41:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you have no interest in such a matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.46,0:41:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like when all power is yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.32,0:41:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody offers you power.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.44,0:41:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask them,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.88,0:41:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,what am I supposed to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.55,0:41:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I got closets full of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.22,0:41:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.09,0:41:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've made some good progress
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.36,0:41:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,since encountering your work,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.92,0:41:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.44,0:41:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I still deal with a lot of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.26,0:41:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.86,0:41:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to label it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.78,0:41:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd call it fear and anxious-type feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.03,0:42:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've taken anti-anxiety medicine in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.11,0:42:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm wondering,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.92,0:42:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,could that constitute a resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.86,0:42:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to experiencing the fear and anxiety?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.40,0:42:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, ideally,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.34,0:42:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you want to get to the bottom of the anxiety, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.96,0:42:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been in psychotherapy, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.11,0:42:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not intensely, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.00,0:42:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like once a week kind of stuff, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.98,0:42:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.53,0:42:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they try and deal, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.88,0:42:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,anxiety means non-specific, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.94,0:42:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,free-flowing anxiety like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.86,0:42:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,or anxiety about something particular?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.98,0:42:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more generalized, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.48,0:42:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's free-flowing anxiety?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.76,0:42:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.82,0:42:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not aware of what the fear is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.44,0:42:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.96,0:42:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the time, right, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.38,0:42:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, most of the time, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.63,0:42:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is your question about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.44,0:43:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the question was,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.24,0:43:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to practice your teaching of not resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.57,0:43:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.13,0:43:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And experiencing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.92,0:43:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.53,0:43:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm wondering,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.63,0:43:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is there a context in which a spiritual seeker
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.55,0:43:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,could take anti-anxiety medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.11,0:43:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,being that that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.11,0:43:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,having...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.96,0:43:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,having the effect of masking the experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.07,0:43:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I would try to extract as much understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.03,0:43:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,as I could out of the anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.46,0:43:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.07,0:43:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Try psychotherapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.80,0:43:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Find an intuitive woman to share it with.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.55,0:43:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they'll intuit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.22,0:43:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Try consciousness calibration,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.63,0:43:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,or have an easy logic research.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.59,0:43:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also everything that's physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.28,0:43:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's also nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.96,0:43:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with taking a tranquilizer
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.92,0:43:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if that assists you in functioning, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.03,0:43:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.40,0:44:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Will that block the awareness?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.46,0:44:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but it may decrease the motivation to find the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.84,0:44:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.44,0:44:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,if it is some mental conflict or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.34,0:44:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll present itself in some other way
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.80,0:44:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in some other time anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.96,0:44:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to disappear even if you tranquilize it, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.63,0:44:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.90,0:44:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.48,0:44:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Inner research,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.72,0:44:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,research within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.38,0:44:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Our day on the couch for a couple of years will help too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.51,0:44:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if there's any psychoanalysts around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.00,0:44:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.96,0:44:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's about to come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.86,0:44:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.96,0:44:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.05,0:44:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.72,0:44:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.53,0:44:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The first being,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.09,0:45:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,from your teachings,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.46,0:45:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I understand that the spirit is eternal
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.17,0:45:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and the bodies wear out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.69,0:45:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had a partner whose body wore out months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.28,0:45:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And some people that care for me and that I love
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.51,0:45:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,have given me information such as
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.28,0:45:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when I dream of him
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.00,0:45:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,or when I think I feel his presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.96,0:45:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If the spirit is eternal,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.24,0:45:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is it possible that you can communicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.03,0:45:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, not even like have a normal conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.01,0:45:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but do you believe that since the spirit is eternal
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.28,0:45:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and life doesn't ever extinguish,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.01,0:45:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that when people's bodies stop moving,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.84,0:45:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that sometimes they can communicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.17,0:45:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is that just spiritual romanticism?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.17,0:45:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're talking about is after death,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.80,0:45:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is his spirit perhaps trying to sometimes come close to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.13,0:45:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.36,0:45:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Or can I feel his presence
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.65,0:45:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and sometimes can I sense him in dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.55,0:45:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is that just spiritual romanticism?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.96,0:45:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I phrasing it correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.30,0:45:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After death, you're wondering,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.03,0:46:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,does his spirit perhaps sometimes come to contact with you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.94,0:46:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,or try to communicate with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.82,0:46:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.17,0:46:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And not even just communicate,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.00,0:46:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,even just be with, sense the presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.88,0:46:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By that, I mean be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.30,0:46:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.22,0:46:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To make known the presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.24,0:46:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to make known to you the presence, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.98,0:46:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.38,0:46:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a possibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.05,0:46:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.61,0:46:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.53,0:46:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.69,0:46:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.96,0:46:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.03,0:46:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.15,0:46:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.65,0:46:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.76,0:46:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.92,0:46:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So not so goofy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.44,0:46:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned it on this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.84,0:46:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.50,0:46:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My other question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.24,0:46:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you intensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.90,0:46:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.65,0:46:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to, when I come to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.05,0:46:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you intensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.32,0:46:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you in February,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.61,0:46:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,no, January in the Sedona,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.13,0:46:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.96,0:46:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you in Phoenix and I saw you a couple of months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.96,0:46:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I get a good night's sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.96,0:47:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I took special vitamins with a lot of B in them this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.96,0:47:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm rested and I'm a morning person,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.96,0:47:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and this has happened every time this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.96,0:47:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I show up and I sit in the audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.96,0:47:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want to hear every word you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.96,0:47:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.96,0:47:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I sleep up until,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.96,0:47:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I slept till lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.96,0:47:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I came back and I started hearing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.96,0:47:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I watch your DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.96,0:47:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read all your books.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.96,0:47:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here because I want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.96,0:47:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.96,0:47:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.96,0:47:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.96,0:47:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't register a conscious kind of thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.96,0:47:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.96,0:47:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.96,0:47:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You picked up the energy of it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.96,0:47:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, you heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.96,0:47:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Three times in a row?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.96,0:47:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you need to know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.96,0:47:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you don't have any memory of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.96,0:47:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowingness will come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.96,0:47:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.96,0:47:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.96,0:47:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.96,0:47:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.96,0:47:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.96,0:47:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
