Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.96,0:48:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.94,0:48:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, I'd like
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.98,0:48:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to express our gratitude for the efforts of your books.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.90,0:48:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made a huge difference in my life personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.92,0:48:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as in the small community I work in,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.92,0:48:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,read power versus force and has made an incredible difference in how we work
