Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.65,0:51:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,consequence has been some people have been able to move further ahead in their
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.29,0:51:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,lives
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.27,0:51:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.15,0:51:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But also, personally, what I've experienced is frustration because sometimes things do
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.23,0:52:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,not happen fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.27,0:52:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the frustration is, you know, your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.71,0:52:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be what you are and allow it to their karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.53,0:52:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Be what you are to them, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.21,0:52:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it isn't just what you say, it's what you become that inspires people.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.86,0:52:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you become the epitome of that which you wish for them, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.05,0:52:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.18,0:52:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.18,0:52:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.18,0:52:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That way it's non-verbal teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.14,0:52:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-verbal teaching, you become the ideal that they incorporate as, in Freudian terminology,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.28,0:52:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.28,0:52:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You become the hero to them, the teacher who cares, the person who is concerned about their
