Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.84,0:52:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.84,0:52:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.84,0:52:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Many a teacher is inspired, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.16,0:52:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.16,0:52:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.16,0:53:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Famous ones, famous teachers, whose classes supposedly hopeless top the academic honors
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.50,0:53:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,list eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.50,0:53:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.50,0:53:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.50,0:53:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, there are some things I do that create so much energy in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.16,0:53:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.16,0:53:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.16,0:53:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.15,0:53:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much energy that I get concerned for my psychological stabilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.15,0:53:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things you do create so much energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.15,0:53:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do.
