Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.15,0:53:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.15,0:53:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just, the energy is so intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.15,0:53:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.15,0:53:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wonder sometimes if it's beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.15,0:53:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.15,0:53:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.15,0:53:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be so crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.15,0:53:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
