Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.63,0:59:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,With this own little karmic path that I have going here, I feel like I'm at a crossroads.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.63,1:00:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've just given up a very lucrative job because I couldn't stand the conflict and the polarity anymore in the politics.
