Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.51,1:06:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,work for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.65,1:06:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the sense especially, recently doing some testing, that sometimes it's more beneficial...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.13,1:06:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I set a limit of, say, 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.63,1:06:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's if the treatment or the modality or whatever didn't calibrate that,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.75,1:06:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't use that for the patient.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.53,1:06:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And in some cases, it seems like they almost get better symptomatic relief,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.67,1:06:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know that's not necessarily a consciousness aspect.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.03,1:06:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I use a lower calibration,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.19,1:06:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe something that's closer to their vibration or calibration.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.23,1:06:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So then here's where the two questions kind of dovetail,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.81,1:06:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,one in my personal life and also with my patients.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.55,1:06:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it something to strive, maybe it's more realistic,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.03,1:06:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,or to encourage calibrated things, whether it be nutrition or books to read,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.07,1:06:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that's in a similar level, or something that's...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.44,1:06:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think everything is physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.65,1:06:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you tell them what you feel would be beneficial physically,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.09,1:07:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,energy-wise, maybe through acupuncture or whatever, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.86,1:07:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Intellectually, through reading, et cetera, spiritual practice,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.13,1:07:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,nutrition.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.92,1:07:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You use everything you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.09,1:07:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what you're really asking is,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.11,1:07:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,if you prescribe something that's far beyond where they're at,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.11,1:07:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,will it have any hold?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.96,1:07:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it have any effect?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.09,1:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say so, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.63,1:07:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, mankind is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.34,1:07:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind is endlessly praying to God,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.90,1:07:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what the level of consciousness, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.36,1:07:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I think the intention behind it, you know, is sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.55,1:07:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, in our personal life...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.42,1:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're trying to tailor it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.73,1:07:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.69,1:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If somebody's in the mid-400s,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.13,1:07:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you should use something that's primarily intellectual
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.07,1:07:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because it'll make sense to them and all.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.05,1:07:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So they come back?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.88,1:07:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they may feel more attracted to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.94,1:07:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I give them a couple of things to do, and, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.53,1:07:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,cafeteria style, try it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.92,1:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, in my personal life,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.63,1:08:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's not so much an object of getting rid of the symptom,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.15,1:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,should I just strive for whatever is the highest calibration?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.59,1:08:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I have a choice of reading one book or the other,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.21,1:08:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,just go with the highest one always?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.03,1:08:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know that I can answer that without studying a specific example.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.01,1:08:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, somebody who calibrates at 250,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.03,1:08:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is it going to help them to read Wang Po at 850?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.72,1:08:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're asking.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.42,1:08:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it going to be meaningful to them?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.88,1:08:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you would say as a teacher, as an educator,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.31,1:08:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,or what your position is,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.47,1:08:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you try to lead them stepwise,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.76,1:08:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,into that which would make kind of sense to them,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.66,1:08:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so they don't end up mystified, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.64,1:08:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.56,1:08:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mantras are good,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.53,1:08:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because you only have to pass kindergarten in order to do them.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.48,1:08:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long and complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.80,1:09:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Something simple and effective, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.80,1:09:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I get your intention is such
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.03,1:09:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that you will certainly find out
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.20,1:09:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,what's going to be the most helpful for this patient,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.60,1:09:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're going to use kinesiology to research that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.98,1:09:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I used to check out the doses of medications I gave people, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.06,1:09:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I would guess 50 milligrams is enough,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.92,1:09:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I would check it out with kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.92,1:09:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would get, yep, 50 milligrams is right, see.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.16,1:09:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Use it to cross-check, you know, cross-check.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.60,1:09:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.22,1:09:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.66,1:09:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.60,1:09:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.48,1:09:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.68,1:09:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,if one commits to a lifestyle of forgiveness towards others
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.98,1:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and surrendering all events to God,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.68,1:09:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,regardless of what happens,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.22,1:09:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,will that commitment eventually lead us
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.90,1:10:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to the level we talked about today, serenity?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.00,1:10:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.60,1:10:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the keystone.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.12,1:10:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.20,1:10:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.38,1:10:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.36,1:10:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell anybody, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.86,1:10:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing to hear it, another thing to do it, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.88,1:10:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But only forgive those who deserve it, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.20,1:10:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The bad guys, they're on their own.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.92,1:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.36,1:10:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You answered my question with a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.60,1:10:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.60,1:10:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a good person.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.60,1:10:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So since Nico is not here, would you do us the honor of leading us in a few long ohms?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.20,1:10:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You want an ohm today?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.20,1:10:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.20,1:10:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, some of us were talking about we'd like not only your ohm, but to lead us
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.20,1:10:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all in an ohm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.20,1:10:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.20,1:10:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think we're going to have to get the ohm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.20,1:10:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have to get the ohm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.20,1:10:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
