Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.06,1:11:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.06,1:12:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I started my journey about 40 years ago, and it seems like you were the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.82,1:12:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,next person, the next teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.82,1:12:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The next teacher, the next person.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.82,1:12:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the next teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.82,1:12:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.06,1:12:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And my husband and I have read your first three books, just finished reading the last
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.06,1:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,one through twice, and would you mind if he took my picture with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.06,1:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants her picture taken with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.06,1:12:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.06,1:12:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pictures are okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.06,1:13:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.81,1:13:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I take one of both of you in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.81,1:13:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I signed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.81,1:13:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.81,1:13:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.81,1:13:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.81,1:13:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we, honey?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.81,1:13:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's taking a picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.81,1:13:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's taking both of us with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.81,1:13:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.81,1:13:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's taking a picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.81,1:13:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He is.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.81,1:13:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.81,1:13:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take one of both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.81,1:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.81,1:13:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.81,1:13:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.81,1:13:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.81,1:13:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.81,1:13:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.81,1:13:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, honey, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.81,1:13:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's bashful.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.81,1:13:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's bashful.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.81,1:13:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's bashful.
