Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.81,1:13:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.81,1:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's mashful.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.81,1:13:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's mashful.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.81,1:13:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.81,1:13:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's five other dwarfs right behind us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.81,1:13:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.77,1:13:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sign
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.31,1:13:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in to the book.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.81,1:14:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.81,1:14:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please speak in a little more detail on the mechanics of intention from two different
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.85,1:14:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,perspectives?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.57,1:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One as it involves an individual.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.05,1:14:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You want clarification on intention?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.19,1:14:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the intention come from the field and then is it energized by the field until the
