Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.76,1:22:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you know to make a success of it or a world-famous
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.19,1:22:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,story
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.34,1:22:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or sell a million copies the the obligation was to write down what you
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.40,1:22:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,knew could you know is seeming of seeming benefit or significance that was
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.22,1:22:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the end of the obligation after that you could croak and not feel guilty about it
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.80,1:22:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,see what I'm saying you're doing it for its own sake and not for some external
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.90,1:22:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,gain to come from it so that verifies the worth of what you're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.19,1:22:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,not by its success but whether you feel that fulfilling your obligation to the
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.09,1:22:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,pee Chen
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.43,1:22:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,doctor Hawkins I'm interested in how would you rate your fictivity is a
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.27,1:22:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,problem solver and as a healer in your psychiatry practice before them medical
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.39,1:23:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,crisis that you had what you practice psychiatry of the years before you had
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.03,1:23:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,a medical crisis that yeah yeah sure when you almost died yeah uh how successful were you
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.72,1:23:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,how successful was your practice oh i always had a successful practice
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.88,1:23:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,before and after you know and when you help people when you help people in their pain
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.38,1:23:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,before your crisis did you ever sense there was a greater power helping you
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.53,1:23:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,helping you heal that person uh i don't know that's in your time i don't recall that i don't
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.47,1:23:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,remember okay that's just curious uh i uh had a good practice before and after you know
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.23,1:23:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of course later on in life i investigated alternate pathways to
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.81,1:23:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,healing you know of course the miracles and things like that which and you know freudian
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.57,1:24:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,psychoanalysis etc was
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.53,1:24:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,my own analyst was an atheist at the time and so was i
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.26,1:24:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and so we were in total agreement about that we have no problem with it
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.72,1:24:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.43,1:24:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,uh freud was my great-grandfather
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.69,1:24:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,my uh my analyst uh my analyst
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.06,1:24:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,was analyzed by abraham carden abraham carden
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.26,1:24:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.46,1:24:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.50,1:24:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.51,1:24:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.53,1:24:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,analyzed by Freud. So
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.46,1:24:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lionel Lovacy, my father,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.22,1:24:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,my grandfather is Cardiner, and my
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.50,1:24:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,great-grandfather is Sigmund Freud.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.39,1:24:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sequoia and Leckley speaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.72,1:24:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're incorrigible.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.51,1:24:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Irrepressible, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.03,1:24:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My spiritual teachers have been
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.56,1:24:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,L.C. Bailey and Rudolf Steiner.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.07,1:25:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,L.C. Bailey and Rudolf Steiner.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.44,1:25:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Alice Bailey, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.30,1:25:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'll add you. Rudolf Steiner, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.38,1:25:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm concerned
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.50,1:25:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,about, well,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.28,1:25:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been really focused on politics
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.48,1:25:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,since all this mess,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.52,1:25:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm concerned about the
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.00,1:25:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic retributions that
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.08,1:25:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,this country will probably suffer.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.74,1:25:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not retribution.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.48,1:25:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the wrong way to phrase it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.88,1:25:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.44,1:25:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That this action causes a retribution.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.38,1:25:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.18,1:25:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,within reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.88,1:25:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything pulls to it
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.40,1:25:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,in accord with that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.65,1:25:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, justice is
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.06,1:25:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,automatic and perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.07,1:25:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.48,1:25:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to pray for
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.78,1:25:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,leaders of all nations
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.80,1:25:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and send them love and light.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.92,1:25:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I just lost my little dog just about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.84,1:25:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost what?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.50,1:25:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My little dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.78,1:25:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've been mourning that quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.44,1:25:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.32,1:25:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.18,1:26:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.50,1:26:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.57,1:26:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.02,1:26:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tired yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.96,1:26:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tired yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.64,1:26:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean, Terry?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.50,1:26:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Restless?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.30,1:26:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what those mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.02,1:26:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.18,1:26:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.20,1:26:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.56,1:26:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.00,1:26:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.42,1:26:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.00,1:26:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the recent lessons was
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.96,1:26:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not speaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.34,1:26:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.78,1:26:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you've invented your inner and outer world.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.65,1:26:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand the inner world
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.88,1:26:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,because it seems like a fantasy
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.40,1:26:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but your outer world
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.32,1:26:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,does that mean by karma and choice
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.88,1:26:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that you've invented it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.78,1:26:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the quote?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.06,1:26:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The inner world and the outer world.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.88,1:27:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you pointing to the Course in Miracles?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.15,1:27:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.90,1:27:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It says
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.24,1:27:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,do you have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.50,1:27:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.53,1:27:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.64,1:27:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.72,1:27:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.78,1:27:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.82,1:27:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.92,1:27:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.00,1:27:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.18,1:27:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what the difference is between the inner and outer world.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.57,1:27:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they mean the outer world.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.78,1:27:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And the world of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.10,1:27:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Civilization, the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.44,1:27:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the world of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.68,1:27:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of the inner world, it's speaking of the world of your mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.70,1:27:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,which is an illusion, it's a fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.96,1:27:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the outer world is the world you visually think you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.84,1:27:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Or that you perceive.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.98,1:27:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.24,1:27:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're talking about Descartes' res interna versus res externa.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.64,1:27:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.88,1:27:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Res cogitans versus, yeah, perception versus essence.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.18,1:27:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the Course in Miracles takes you beyond projecting perception
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.00,1:27:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you can comprehend essence.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.74,1:27:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.26,1:27:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The miracle is that what is perceived is transformed in time and significance and meaning.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.68,1:27:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you see the essence.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.30,1:28:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you see the essence, that's miraculous
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.98,1:28:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,because you realize then,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.28,1:28:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.57,1:28:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.60,1:28:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The transformation is by the replacement of the linear content by context.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.26,1:28:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember you see a bird of prey eating the sparrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.40,1:28:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And then through the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.74,1:28:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that the sparrow,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.18,1:28:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual evolution is by serving that which is higher.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.76,1:28:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.64,1:28:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We all serve that which we sacrifice the lesser for the greater.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.80,1:28:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thereby do we earn the karma to become the greater.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.40,1:28:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the animal world serves us.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.68,1:28:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But to see that is miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.57,1:28:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To thee, O Lord, do I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.78,1:29:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because to the animal world, we are the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.18,1:29:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To thee, O Lord, do I surrender my beingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.07,1:29:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the animal spirit thereby becomes transformed
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.18,1:29:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and karmically earns the right to become the human.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.68,1:29:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.18,1:29:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What I just stated is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.18,1:29:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That is also the teaching of the Rig Veda.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.18,1:29:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rig Veda.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.18,1:29:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That all lives to sacrifice itself to that which is the higher.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.68,1:29:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And by sacrificing itself,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.72,1:29:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to the higher,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.72,1:29:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it karmically earns the right to become the higher.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.72,1:29:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the gift to the cattle.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.72,1:29:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The gift to the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.72,1:29:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The gift to the ducks.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.72,1:29:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So we love the animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.72,1:29:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because on some intuitive level,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.72,1:29:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we know that there is somehow one with us
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.72,1:29:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in some kind of a concordant karmic evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.72,1:29:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.72,1:29:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for asking.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.72,1:30:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.72,1:30:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.72,1:30:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.72,1:30:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.72,1:30:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.72,1:30:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.72,1:30:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.72,1:30:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Robert.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.72,1:30:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want everybody to know Robert.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.72,1:30:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's terrific.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.72,1:30:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrific.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.72,1:30:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Very significant person.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.72,1:30:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.72,1:30:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.72,1:30:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering if you can explain a little bit more
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.72,1:30:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the mechanism of surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.72,1:30:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mechanism?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.72,1:30:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk about it as a shortcut. It makes sense, but it's something that's never been fully explained.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.10,1:30:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is to surrender?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.98,1:30:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with volition, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.32,1:30:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To let be what it is. This comes out of humility.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.42,1:30:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the reason for it, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.98,1:30:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't know the reason for it doesn't mean that it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.68,1:31:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This applies to everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.72,1:31:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In the world, including war, suicide, death, starvation, plague, volcanic eruptions, tsunamis.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.00,1:31:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is not explicable to human reason, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.32,1:31:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that it's not explicable to human reason is indicative of the fact that you aren't God, you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.10,1:31:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So we surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.07,1:31:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The significance and the meaning of this to Almighty God
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.14,1:31:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.72,1:31:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to Divine Wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.72,1:31:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So we substitute Divine Wisdom for
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.50,1:31:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,for
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.57,1:31:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,an egoistic opinion, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.72,1:31:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's to say that it should not happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.72,1:31:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling God it should not happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.42,1:31:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.92,1:31:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution of humanity for three million years out of the emergent hominid
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.42,1:31:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that it shouldn't happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.81,1:32:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you telling by your opinion that it should be different than it is, you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.81,1:32:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And on what basis, what kind of contextualization of reality would allow you to make such a statement, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.81,1:32:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's first?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.81,1:32:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.81,1:32:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.81,1:32:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to grasp the essence.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.81,1:32:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So surrender means to let go, surrender one's personal will
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.81,1:32:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to the sovereignty of divinity, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.81,1:32:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To let go of outcomes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.81,1:32:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know the reasons why such things happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.81,1:32:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing, you see, is the emergence of a propensity.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.81,1:32:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The emergence of a propensity.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.81,1:32:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And some things can only be learned through pain that is of such severity that you hit bottom.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.81,1:32:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it take for mankind to give up war as an option to salute sovereignty?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.81,1:33:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And to salute solving problems, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.81,1:33:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it takes is whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.81,1:33:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In the self-help groups, they talk about hitting bottom.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.81,1:33:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's high bottoms and there's low bottoms.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.81,1:33:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,High bottoms get it right away without having to experience it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.81,1:33:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Low bottoms...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.81,1:33:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,30 million people starve to death based on a certain ideology.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.81,1:33:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that sufficient?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.81,1:33:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that sufficient to shake your faith in that ideology?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.81,1:33:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are many adherents still today walking this earth
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.81,1:33:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that think Mayo's Little Red Book is the hottest thing going.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.81,1:33:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.81,1:33:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,30 million people dying of starvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.81,1:33:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.81,1:33:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.81,1:33:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a Frisbee and you're supposed to sign it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.81,1:33:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to sign it?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.81,1:33:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.81,1:33:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.81,1:33:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That is funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.81,1:34:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.81,1:34:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.81,1:34:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sign it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.81,1:34:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sign it here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.81,1:34:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we talked about that Frisbee in Toronto, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.81,1:34:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.81,1:34:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog chasing the Frisbee.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.81,1:34:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave the dog's name the way it was in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.81,1:34:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So somebody emails that his name was something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.81,1:34:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Elvis in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.81,1:34:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Elvis in the paper, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.81,1:34:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Elvis.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.81,1:34:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Elvis calibrated over 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.81,1:34:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares what the dog's name is?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.81,1:34:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And precipitated a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.81,1:34:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.81,1:34:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So we will go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.81,1:34:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both so much for helping us.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.81,1:34:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I read Glamour, Alice Bailey's book that you recommended.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.81,1:34:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And do you recommend her other books?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.81,1:34:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.81,1:34:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.81,1:34:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.81,1:34:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.81,1:34:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise I'll have to read all of her books and decide which one to recommend.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.81,1:34:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.81,1:35:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The projection of the energy field of specialness is what adds glamour and attraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.81,1:35:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's Hollywood's, you know, what it lives on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.81,1:35:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of glamour.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.81,1:35:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.81,1:35:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I love your laugh, first of all.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.81,1:35:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When you talk about self with a capital S, are you talking about the soul?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.81,1:35:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.81,1:35:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.81,1:35:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The essence, the source of it, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.81,1:35:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.81,1:35:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then my other question is why do some people remember their past lives while others
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.81,1:35:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,do not?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.81,1:35:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And why is the amnesia important when we're reincarnating?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.81,1:35:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.81,1:35:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.81,1:35:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you incarnate, you instantly forget previous incarnations.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.81,1:35:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.81,1:35:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because now you're this body and you're in this present.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.81,1:35:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You identify with the current perception.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.81,1:35:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.81,1:35:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you're out of body, you're not limited that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.81,1:36:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's an amnesia the minute you incarnate.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.81,1:36:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an amnesia the minute you incarnate.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.81,1:36:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.81,1:36:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Above level 600 or so, you can begin to recall.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.81,1:36:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.81,1:36:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.81,1:36:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And the recall is not of a memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.81,1:36:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The recall is of the subjective experiencing of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.81,1:36:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.81,1:36:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.81,1:36:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.81,1:36:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.81,1:36:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what does the body of a blacksmith feels like?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.81,1:36:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because to go back into that lifetime, I am like the ultimate mesomorph.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.81,1:36:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.81,1:36:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got huge biceps.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.81,1:36:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that life and I know what happened to that life.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.81,1:36:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.81,1:36:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.81,1:36:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.81,1:36:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, don't you remember it like a vivid memory?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.81,1:36:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.81,1:36:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like a body memory or a...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.81,1:36:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.81,1:36:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like you relive it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.81,1:36:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.81,1:36:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.81,1:36:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's hypnotics, very simple past life recall techniques.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.81,1:36:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.81,1:37:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You calm yourself down, transport yourself back to asking the question, and you get off
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.81,1:37:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,at the 14th floor, and that life begins to rerun experientially like it's happening now.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.81,1:37:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like a movie where you witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.81,1:37:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the re-experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.81,1:37:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.81,1:37:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see the horse's hoofs come up.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.81,1:37:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.81,1:37:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you remember how you died in that lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.81,1:37:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And why you and horses ain't never got along.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.81,1:37:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My other question is, are we born with our time of death?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.81,1:37:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read that before.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.81,1:37:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.81,1:37:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.81,1:37:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've calibrated that many times, and that's so.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.81,1:37:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.81,1:37:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.81,1:37:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.81,1:37:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.81,1:37:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.81,1:37:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Every videotape comes with a story.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.81,1:37:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.81,1:37:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.81,1:37:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.81,1:37:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.81,1:37:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Every videotape comes to an end, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.81,1:37:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins and Susan, for being here and your staff.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.81,1:38:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.81,1:38:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Two months ago at this seminar, you gave us an exercise you called the counting exercise
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.31,1:38:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,about eating 60 cookies a day and counting them.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.81,1:38:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, counting them.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.81,1:38:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.81,1:38:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I loved that exercise.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.81,1:38:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.81,1:38:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.81,1:38:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And you mentioned that I'm up to 80 cookies a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.81,1:38:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm up to 80 cookies a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.81,1:38:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you mentioned that is a principle of the Heisenberg principle.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.81,1:38:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The observation begins to change the phenomena, and, well, the best technique for, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.81,1:38:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the most successful one was called, I don't know, Tobacco Anonymous or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.81,1:38:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And all they did is have you count the number of cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.81,1:38:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.81,1:38:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then everybody in the class eventually quit smoking, you know, just to become conscious,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.81,1:38:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,conscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.81,1:38:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.81,1:38:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, my question is, is it, you're, in the case of the cookies, you're looking at the
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.81,1:39:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,cookie, which is a negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.81,1:39:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.81,1:39:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a negative?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.81,1:39:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.81,1:39:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The cookie's not negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.81,1:39:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, so where does the wave come in?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.81,1:39:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What, where, what's collapsing?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.81,1:39:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it, is there a wave between the cookie and me?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.81,1:39:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The observation.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.81,1:39:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to have the last lecture to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.81,1:39:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with intention, intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.81,1:39:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, merely observing a phenomena begins to change it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.81,1:39:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, witnessing the phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.81,1:39:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do you clear your throat every time you're giving a lecture, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.81,1:39:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.81,1:39:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, the more you become aware of that, now you have some control of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.81,1:39:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.81,1:39:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.81,1:39:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more aware.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.81,1:39:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.19,1:39:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you become more conscious and aware.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.96,1:39:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.15,1:39:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.05,1:39:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You learned that in third grade.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.96,1:40:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong, wrong, wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.92,1:40:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a 60 on this test.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.85,1:40:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.88,1:40:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all you've done, first of all, and second of all.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.19,1:40:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My first question is, on the animal chart of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.07,1:40:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed, and you said, that below the level of 200 are basically carnivores.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.22,1:40:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Generally, generally, generally.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.50,1:40:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.93,1:40:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And then above the level of 200 are...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.27,1:40:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Generally.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.89,1:40:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Generally.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.43,1:40:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not written in cement.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.46,1:40:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get you into a sense of compulsive literalism or concretism, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.42,1:40:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.05,1:40:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Songbirds are less than 200, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.00,1:40:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, then, as humans,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.18,1:40:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,could we raise our level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.50,1:40:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,by being more aware of our own consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.07,1:40:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By being vegetarian.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.73,1:40:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,By being what?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.96,1:40:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegetarian.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.10,1:40:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not eating meat.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.72,1:40:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegetarianism calibrates about 205.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.07,1:40:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not, you know, a little sort of disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.42,1:40:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a vegetarian for, you know, a good 10 years or so.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.01,1:40:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And, actually, one day I was in a restaurant
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.69,1:41:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and it came to me that I am meat.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.27,1:41:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I am meat.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.50,1:41:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You are meat, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.07,1:41:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a vegetarian.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.46,1:41:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.81,1:41:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was previously.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.85,1:41:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was for 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.03,1:41:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For a while, not 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.61,1:41:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.93,1:41:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've been considering it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.34,1:41:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been reading some Buddhism and...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.89,1:41:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think it's very fine to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.47,1:41:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.65,1:41:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.47,1:41:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.51,1:41:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And one other...
