Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.07,1:41:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a new one.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.80,1:41:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you read the Rig Vita and then ask me again next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.72,1:41:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.10,1:41:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rig Vita.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.93,1:41:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,R-I-G Vita.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.64,1:41:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.50,1:42:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates about 900.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.68,1:42:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one more quick question, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.73,1:42:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed you had Plato on your list of...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.92,1:42:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This would be authors, I believe,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.47,1:42:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and you rated their consciousness level or something,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.64,1:42:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of their works.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.77,1:42:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.55,1:42:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.92,1:42:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.07,1:42:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right below that was Plotinus.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.11,1:42:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if you could rate Plotinus as the man,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.76,1:42:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,like with the testing.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.51,1:42:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Test where he would be as a man as opposed to his works.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.35,1:42:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.31,1:42:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Plotinus.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.77,1:42:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be different.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.00,1:42:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be different, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.01,1:42:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's Plotinus as a spiritual teacher,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.42,1:42:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's Plotinus as an author.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.07,1:42:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.81,1:42:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As a spiritually evolved person,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.34,1:42:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,his calibration is higher than his writings.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.81,1:42:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.34,1:42:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just curious if you knew what that was.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.88,1:42:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.14,1:42:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.60,1:42:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think his writings were 503, but I think Plotinus...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.98,1:42:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,502, 503.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.11,1:42:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, around in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.86,1:42:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The author.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.88,1:42:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the author.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.24,1:42:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.76,1:42:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.16,1:42:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Plotinus as an author was about five...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.30,1:42:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking about Plotinus as the spiritual teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.50,1:43:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.22,1:43:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Plotinus as an author calibrates around 503, 504.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.53,1:43:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Plotinus as a realized mystic calibrates over 700, 720.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.14,1:43:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.48,1:43:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See, many people wrote up to a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.76,1:43:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you bliss out.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.82,1:43:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the writing.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.86,1:43:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you've got a good wife,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.22,1:43:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you're never going to write anything again.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.00,1:43:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.50,1:43:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
