Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.57,1:43:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.00,1:43:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.44,1:43:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.14,1:43:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
